उत्साह utsāh _mu_ zeal, enthusiasm [भारी great, साधारण ordinary]; ~ जगाना/भरना to enthuse, to inspire zeal; ~ पाना to receive encouragement; ~ भंग करना to discourage, to demoralize. [syn. जोश] 
उत्साहहीन utsāh·hīn _a_ dispirited, down-hearted [जनता public, व्यक्‍ित person, सेना army, सैनिक soldier]; ~ होना to become --/demoralized. 
