उदासी udāsī _fu_ sadness, dejection; सब पर ~ छा गई all were clouded with --; चारों ओर ~ बरसती थी gloom clouded all sides. 
उदासीन udāsīn _a_ indifferent, dis- interested [पक्ष party, भागीदार partner, मित्र ally]; वह इस मामले में ~ है he is disinterested in (indifferent towards) this affair; संसार (परिवार) से ~ detached from the world (family). 
