उस us **1**. _pron_ [obl. sing. of वह] that; ~ का his, her, its; ~ का तोता (बच्चा, भाई, रोना) his/her parrot (child, brother, weeping); ~ की कमीज़ (माँ, बहनें, हँसी) his/her shirt (mother, sisters, smile); ~ के काग़ज़ (बेटे, मालिक) his/her papers (sons, masters); ~ के नाम पर in his/her name; ~ के पास near it/him/her; ~ के आगे ahead of it, in front of him/her; ~ के बिना without him/her; ~ के बारे में about him; ~ पर मत हँसो don'tlaugh at him/her; उसको (to) him/her/it; ~ को दे दो give it to him/her; ~ से by/with/from him; उसमें in that, therein; उस विषय में in that connection. **2**. _a_ that; ~ दिन that day; ~ समय at that time. [see इस, इन] 
