खिचड़ी khich·ṛī **I**. _fu_ (_a_) khichri, mixed preparation of rice and pulses; ~ पकाना (बनाना, खाना, देना) cook (prepare, eat, serve) --; △ ~ पकाना to conspire, to hatch a plot. (_b_) hotch-potch; तुमने सब ~ कर डाला you have mixed up everything. **II**. _a_ mixed; ~ दाढ़ी beard with a sprinkling of gray hair; ~ बाल a sprinkling of gray hair; ~ भाषा mixed lauguage. 
