घटित ghaṭit ~ होना to occur, to take place; एक घटना ~ हूई an event/incident occurred (took place); ऐसा एक बार ~ हुआ it occurred/happened once. 
घटिया ghaṭiyā _a_ [unchangeable] of low quality or standard, inferior [कपड़ा cloth, काग़ज़ paper, गेहूँ wheat, माल goods, लेखक writer, चीज़ें things]; ये संतरे उनसे घटिया हैं these oranges are inferior to those. [ant. ब़ढ़िया] 
