घुन ghun _mc_ wood-worm, weevil; लकड़ी या अनाज को घुन खा/लग जाता है wood or grain is eaten by --. △ ~ लगना to be in the grip of canker, to suffer decay: उसको चिंता का ~ लग गया he was suffering from the canker of worry. 
घुनना ghun·nā _vi_ (_a_) to be eaten by a wood-worm/weevil; अलमारी घुन गई the almirah was eaten by weevils. (_b_) (fig.) उसका शरीर घुन रहा है his body is decaying (from inside). 
