चंदा chandā _mc_ (_a_) subscription [मासिक monthly, वार्षिक yearly]; ~ करना to collect/raise --; ~ देना to pay --, to subscribe: हम सबने क्लब का -- दिया we all subscribed to the club; पत्रिका का ~ -- of the magazine. (_b_) premium (for an insurance policy): बीमा का छमाही ~ six-monthly -- for insurance. 
चंद्र chandra _mu_ [usually in compounds including proper names] moon; ~ कला phase of the moon; ~ किरण moon-beam; ~ - ग्रहण lunar eclipse; ~ प्रभा moon- light; ~ मुखी moon-faced; कृष्णचन्द्र, रामचंद्र, गोपालचंद्र, चंद्रप्रकाश, चंद्रगुप्त, चंद्रभान, _etc_. names of persons. 
चंद्रमा chandramā _mu_ [formal use] moon = चाँद [more common]. 
चंपत champat _a_ [predicative] disappeared, vanished: न जाने साइकल कैसे ~ हो गया Don't know how the bicycle has disappeared; लड़का ~ हो गया the boy took to his heels (vanished). [syn. ग़ायब] 
