छी chhī _int_ = छिः q. v. 
छीछालेदार chhīchhāledar _fu_ humiliation: किसी की ~ उड़ाना (करना) to humiliate smb, to put smb to --; किसी की ~ हुई smb was humiliated, someone was put to --. [syn. दुर्गत] 
