जहाँ jahã _adv_ where: जहाँ चाहो जाओ go where you like; यह वही जगह है जहाँ हम मिले थे this is the place where we had met. ~ कहीं wherever: ~ कहीं वे गये लोगों ने उनका स्वागत किया -- he went people welcomed him. ~ का तहाँ at the same place as before: वह ~ का तहाँ खेल रहा है he is playing at the place where he was before; ये चीज़ें ~ की तहाँ रख दो put these things as they were. ~ -जहाँ wheresoever: ~ -जहाँ हम गये -- we went ... ~ तक as far as: ~ तक हो सके as far as possible; ~ तक मेरा सवाल है as far as I am concerned. ~ तहाँ here& there, everywhere: मैंने उसे ~ तहाँ ढूँढ़ा I looked for him --. ~ से from where, whence; ~ से वह आया था from -- he had come. 
