टूटना ṭūṭ·nā _vi_ (_a_) to break, to be broken: टहनी (घड़ी, हड्डी) टूट गई the twig (watch, bone) was broken; दिल टूट गया heart was broken; टूटा हुआ दिल broken heart; हाथ टूट गया the hand was fractured. (_b_) △ अंग ~ to feel exhausted. घमंड टूटा pride was shattered; ध्यान टूटा attention was disrupted; नींद टूट गई sleep was disturbed; संबंध टूट गया the connection was  severed; स्कूल टूट गया the school was demolished; टूटा पैसा change (of money). [_vt_ तोड़ना] 
