टेढ़ा ṭeṛhā _a_ (_a_) skew, curved; ~ बाँस -- bamboo; टेढ़ी लकीर curved line; ~ करना to bend; ~ होना to bend, to be curved, △ to be angry. (_b_) zigzag, irregular: ~रास्ता -- path. (_c_) difficult, intricate [काम job, मामला affair, सवाल question]; △ टेढ़ी आँख से देखना to see with an angry look; टेढ़ी खीर a difficult and rather impossible task. 
