निश्चिंतता nishchint·tā _fu_ freedom from care/worry: जब तक वह न आया तब तक मुझे ~ नहीं थीं I did not have -- until he came. 
निश्चित nishchit _a_ (_a_) definite [उत्तर answer, उद्देश्य purpose, मत opinion, समय time, स्थान place]; कुछ भी ~ नहीं है there is nothing --. (_b_) fixed, appointed: ~ समय के भीतर within the -- time; ~ करना to fix: तिथि ~ करना to fix a date. (_c_) decided, settled:पहले ले ~ -- beforehand, already --; सब बातें ~ हो गईं everything was --; ~ रुप से certainly, decidedly. [syn. पक्का] 
