ने ne _agentive termination_ [used with a subject governed by a transitive verb in past tense] आशा ने फल खाया Asha ate a fruit; उसने कबूतर मारा he/she killed a pigeon; मैंने कहा I said; मैंने कहा है I have said; मैंनें कहा था I had said; मैंने कहा होगा I might have said. 
