पल्ला pallā _mc_ **1**. hem, extremity: धोती या चादर का ~ -- of a dhoti or sheet. △ से ~ छूटना to be rid of, to be absolved from: इस दुष्ट या ज़िम्मेदारी से मेरा ~ छूटा I have got rid of this wretched fellow, I am absolved of this responsibility; किसी का ~ पकड़ना to seek support from smb; किसी के आगे ~ पसारना to seek favours from smb; कोई चीज़ पल्ले पड़ना to be condemned to have smth; पल्ले बाँधना to take care, to remember: मेरी बात अपने पल्ले बाँध लो mind my words; पल्ले होना toposses some money; मेरे पल्ले कुछ नहीं बचा I have been left with nothing. **2**. = पलड़ा. 
