पहर pahar _mc_ a measure of time equal to three hours: दिन-रात में आठ ~ होते हैं there are eight pahars in day and night; अगले ~ in the fore-noon; पिछले ~ in the evening; दो ~ noon; तीसरे ~ in the after-noon. 
