-बद्ध -baddha _suff_. bound [as in] वचनबद्ध bound by promise; प्रतिज्ञा- बद्ध bound in vow; नियमबद्ध regulated; सीमाबद्ध bound by limitations;  करबद्ध with folded hands; पंक्‍ितबद्ध in a line; भाषाबद्ध expressed in language; _etc_.    बद्ध baddha- _pref_. bound: बद्धकोष्ठ bound in bowels, constipated; बद्धांजलि with folded hands, _etc_. 
