बिछना bichh·nā _vi_ (_a_) to be spread: बिस्तर बिछ गई the bed was spread; दरीयाँ बिछ गईं carpets were spread. (_b_) to be laid: ज़मीन के नीचे तार बिछ गए cables were laid under the ground. [cf. फैलना] 
