बेहतर beh·tar _a_ [pedantic] better [चीज़ें things, लोग people, हालत condition]; ~ करना/बनाना to better: किसी की हालत ~ बनाना to better smb's condition. 
बेहद behad _adv_ boundless(ly), extremely [ख़ुश happy, ज़रूरी necessary, मुश्किल difficult]; वे ~ धीरे चल रहे थे they were walking ~ slowly; आपकी ~ मेहरबानी है it is -- kind of you; मैं उससे ~ नाराज़ हूँ I am -- angry with him/her. 
बेहोश behosh _a_ unconscious, senseless = बेसुध ~ होना to faint: यह सुनकर वह ~ हो गई she fainted on hearing this. [syn. अचेत, बेख़बर] 
