लजाना lajānā **I**. _vi_ (_a_) to feel shy, to blush: लड़की लजाती है the girl feels shy. (_b_) to be ashamed: यह सुनकर मैं लजा गई I was ashamed on hearing this. **II**. _vt_ to make one blush/ashamed: मैंने उसे लजाया I ashamed him/her, I made him/her blush. [syn. शरमाना] 
