लिखा-पढ़ी likhā-paṛhī _fu_ (_a_) written negotiations: दोनों दलों के बीच में ~ चल रही हैं -- are going on between the two parties; ~ करना to negotiate in writing. (_b_) correspondence: प्रति दिन बहुत ~ करनी पड़ती है a lot of -- has to be done every day. 
