वास्ता vāstā _mu_ concern, relation: मेरा उससे कोई ~ नहीं I have no -- with him/her/it; I have nothing to do with him/her/it; किसी से ~ पड़ना to have to deal with smb; ~ रखना to have -- with; अपने काम से ~ रखो concern yourself with your own business. [syn. सरोकार, संबंध] 
