विदा vidā _fu_ farewell, leave: ~ करना to bid farewell, to see off: हम उसे ~ करने स्टेशन पर गये we went to the station to see him off; ~ लेना to take leave, to bid farewell: मैंने मित्रों से ~ ली और चल पड़ा I took leave of my friends (I bade farewell to my friends) and started off; ~ होना to take leave, to depart: हम कालेज से or उन लोगों से दस बजे ~ हुए we departed from that place या took leave of those people at 10 o'clock. 
