सो so **I**. _pron_ that, it, he, she [according to context]; जो बोये सो काटे he who sows shall reap; ~ तो ठीक है that of course is all right; ~ क्या what of that ? **II**. thus, therefore, then: ~ मैं क्या करूँ then what should I do ? 
